title: My fanmade Blood Moon Pyke lol

embed.description: My fanmade Blood Moon Pyke for League of Legends. Concepts and Slash Art.

body:
Heyo, I just wanted to share my own fanmade Blood Moon Pyke that I've designed for the past 2 months. I never knew that Riot was making one as well until they announced it on 5th December.  LoL What is the coincidence? 

My insta: https://www.instagram.com/crimsonsealart/

replies.body: I love the composition here - so intimidating and atmospheric! Very cool. :D
Honestly can't tell if I like Riots version or yours, yours looks a lot more noticeable
